Nigerien Parliament Adopts Legislation Granting Amnesty to Military Junta

-- B y   D j i b r i l   S a i d o u
-- 
2011-05-18T23:59:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-18/nigerien-parliament-adopts-legislation-granting-amnesty-to-military-junta.html
Niger’s parliament today adopted a
law granting amnesty to the country’s military junta, which is
helping restore civilian rule after taking power last year.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
